{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"The Experience of Making A Short&nbsp;Film","content":"<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><a href=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/02/09/the-experience-of-making-a-short-film/\"><img data-attachment-id=\"817\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/02/09/the-experience-of-making-a-short-film/desk/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/desk.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"2048,1366\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Agnij Sur&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"desk\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/desk.jpg?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/desk.jpg?w=700\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-817 size-large\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/desk.jpg?w=700&#038;h=467\" alt=\"desk\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/desk.jpg?w=700&amp;h=467 700w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/desk.jpg?w=1400&amp;h=934 1400w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/desk.jpg?w=150&amp;h=100 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/desk.jpg?w=450&amp;h=300 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/desk.jpg?w=768&amp;h=512 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"   /></a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Let&#8217;s do something. How about movies?</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">~Sreyan Mullick Chowdhury.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Sreyan talked me into something I was originally uninterested in. <!--more-->Ever since I have known him, he&#8217;s been enthusiastic. Some people have questioned his abilities. But after being his friend for four years, I&#8217;ve understood something. He&#8217;s a person <strong>full </strong>of potential, and capable of a <strong>lot of things</strong>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em>The Anon. Productions</em> happens to be one of his dream projects. It was <strong>our </strong>dream project. Now, it&#8217;s transformed into something else. It has expanded. It has more members, who each specialize in different fields. It&#8217;s a working production house. And quite recently, it produced a short film.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">This post is about how we brought into existence a movie based on the theme <strong>&#8216;Then and Now&#8217;.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Courier New';\">If you want to skip to the short film, click <a href=\"#movie\">here</a>.</span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">I won&#8217;t narrate in detail about what happened during each day. I&#8217;ll give you a gist.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The first 3 days were spent on shooting the video. Here are some pictures, from the &#8216;shooting days&#8217; :</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_819\" style=\"width: 710px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"819\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/02/09/the-experience-of-making-a-short-film/fixing-camera/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/fixing-camera.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"960,571\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Picasa&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1423430468&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"fixing camera\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/fixing-camera.jpg?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/fixing-camera.jpg?w=700\" class=\"wp-image-819 size-large\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/fixing-camera.jpg?w=700&#038;h=417\" alt=\"fixing camera\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/fixing-camera.jpg?w=700&amp;h=417 700w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/fixing-camera.jpg?w=150&amp;h=89 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/fixing-camera.jpg?w=450&amp;h=268 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/fixing-camera.jpg?w=768&amp;h=457 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/fixing-camera.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"   /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Shooting the &#8216;black and white portion&#8217; of the film</figcaption></figure>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_816\" style=\"width: 450px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"816\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/02/09/the-experience-of-making-a-short-film/crazy-agnij-sreyan/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/crazy-agnij-sreyan.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"540,960\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"crazy agnij sreyan\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/crazy-agnij-sreyan.jpg?w=450&#038;h=800\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/crazy-agnij-sreyan.jpg?w=394\" class=\"wp-image-816\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/crazy-agnij-sreyan.jpg?w=450&#038;h=800\" alt=\"crazy agnij sreyan\" width=\"450\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/crazy-agnij-sreyan.jpg?w=450&amp;h=800 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/crazy-agnij-sreyan.jpg?w=84&amp;h=150 84w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/crazy-agnij-sreyan.jpg?w=253&amp;h=450 253w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/crazy-agnij-sreyan.jpg 540w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sreyan with Agnij [behind the camera] <strong>*craziness*</strong></figcaption></figure>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><img data-attachment-id=\"853\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/02/09/the-experience-of-making-a-short-film/in-shoot/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/in-shoot.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"960,720\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"in shoot\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/in-shoot.jpg?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/in-shoot.jpg?w=700\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-853\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/in-shoot.jpg?w=700&#038;h=525\" alt=\"in shoot\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/in-shoot.jpg?w=700&amp;h=525 700w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/in-shoot.jpg?w=150&amp;h=113 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/in-shoot.jpg?w=450&amp;h=338 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/in-shoot.jpg?w=768&amp;h=576 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/in-shoot.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"   /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">I wasn&#8217;t involved during these days. The last two days (before the submission date) were critical to me.</p>\n<hr />\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify;\">Day 4 (21<sup>st</sup> of January, 2015):</h3>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">My college ended at 5:00 PM. I went home and set up the condenser microphone, the stand, and connected the microphone to my laptop.</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_832\" style=\"width: 500px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"832\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/02/09/the-experience-of-making-a-short-film/dhanolti-1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/dhanolti-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1080,1080\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Nabhoneel&#039;s\\rPhotos&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS REBEL T3&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1421895831&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;18&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;3200&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.125&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Dhanolti-1\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/dhanolti-1.jpg?w=500&#038;h=500\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/dhanolti-1.jpg?w=700\" class=\"wp-image-832\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/dhanolti-1.jpg?w=500&#038;h=500\" alt=\"All ready\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/dhanolti-1.jpg?w=500&amp;h=500 500w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/dhanolti-1.jpg?w=1000&amp;h=1000 1000w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/dhanolti-1.jpg?w=150&amp;h=150 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/dhanolti-1.jpg?w=450&amp;h=450 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/dhanolti-1.jpg?w=768&amp;h=768 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/dhanolti-1.jpg?w=700&amp;h=700 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">All ready</figcaption></figure>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The short film would contain no conversations (among the actors). Narration, foley sounds and music &#8211; these would be contributing to the &#8216;audio&#8217; of the movie. Nilanjan, the co-writer and the co-director would be narrating for the movie. He came to my house at 8 PM. He read the lines to himself again and again to get the proper emotions in his voice. Sreyan and Avishek were editing the video files at Avishek&#8217;s house.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><img data-attachment-id=\"831\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/02/09/the-experience-of-making-a-short-film/screenshot_premier-pro/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/screenshot_premier-pro.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1024,768\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"screenshot_premier pro\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/screenshot_premier-pro.jpg?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/screenshot_premier-pro.jpg?w=700\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-831 size-large\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/screenshot_premier-pro.jpg?w=700&#038;h=525\" alt=\"screenshot_premier pro\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/screenshot_premier-pro.jpg?w=700&amp;h=525 700w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/screenshot_premier-pro.jpg?w=150&amp;h=113 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/screenshot_premier-pro.jpg?w=450&amp;h=338 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/screenshot_premier-pro.jpg?w=768&amp;h=576 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/screenshot_premier-pro.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"   /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">We were communicating via Skype.</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_808\" style=\"width: 710px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"808\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/02/09/the-experience-of-making-a-short-film/skype/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/skype1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1366,768\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"skype\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/skype1.jpg?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/skype1.jpg?w=700\" class=\"size-large wp-image-808\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/skype1.jpg?w=700&#038;h=393\" alt=\"Sreyan [right] and Avishek\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/skype1.jpg?w=700&amp;h=393 700w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/skype1.jpg?w=150&amp;h=84 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/skype1.jpg?w=450&amp;h=253 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/skype1.jpg?w=768&amp;h=432 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/skype1.jpg 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"   /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sreyan [right] and Avishek</figcaption></figure>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>At 12:30 AM, Nilanjan was ready</strong>. I set the microphone to his level. He then narrated. Our work was completed at 3:00 AM. Nilanjan perfected himself within three takes. But there was slight noise in the background, and the sound needed to be crisp. Coupled with that, I&#8217;m not an expert at mastering and editing. I did my best.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><img data-attachment-id=\"830\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/02/09/the-experience-of-making-a-short-film/screenshot_audition/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/screenshot_audition.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1366,768\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"screenshot_audition\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/screenshot_audition.jpg?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/screenshot_audition.jpg?w=700\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-830\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/screenshot_audition.jpg?w=700&#038;h=393\" alt=\"screenshot_audition\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/screenshot_audition.jpg?w=700&amp;h=393 700w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/screenshot_audition.jpg?w=150&amp;h=84 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/screenshot_audition.jpg?w=450&amp;h=253 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/screenshot_audition.jpg?w=768&amp;h=432 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/screenshot_audition.jpg 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"   /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">And the end product, although produced at a late hour, wasn&#8217;t so bad 🙂</p>\n<hr />\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify;\">Day 2 [The Final day before submission &#8211; 22<sup>nd</sup> of January, 2015]</h3>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Video editing had been completed during the previous night by Sreyan and Avishek</strong>. Meanwhile, after completing our work on the narration, I had sent the audio files to them. Sreyan had positioned the narration properly (in the video). What was left was the foley sounds, and the music. Frankly, I was too scared to even think of how to do it. We had absolutely <strong>no </strong>knowledge on how to make foley sounds.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After attending college, Sreyan and I boarded a bus and came to my home. We were tired. The previous night, Sreyan had had <strong>no rest</strong>. I had slept for 3 hours. The tension however, drove the sleep away. We set up the microphone, the laptop, and started our job.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">We noted down the scenes that required folly. And I created a preset on Audition after recording a &#8216;typing foley&#8217;.</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_833\" style=\"width: 710px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"833\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/02/09/the-experience-of-making-a-short-film/dhanolti-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/dhanolti-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1620,1080\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Nabhoneel&#039;s\\rPhotos&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS REBEL T3&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1421955839&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;24&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;3200&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.066666666666667&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Dhanolti-2\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/dhanolti-2.jpg?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/dhanolti-2.jpg?w=700\" class=\"size-large wp-image-833\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/dhanolti-2.jpg?w=700&#038;h=467\" alt=\"Practicing\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/dhanolti-2.jpg?w=700&amp;h=467 700w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/dhanolti-2.jpg?w=1400&amp;h=934 1400w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/dhanolti-2.jpg?w=150&amp;h=100 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/dhanolti-2.jpg?w=450&amp;h=300 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/dhanolti-2.jpg?w=768&amp;h=512 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"   /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Practicing</figcaption></figure>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">We spent an hour deciding how to get the other parts done. Moreover, we would have to wait till everyone was asleep in the house, because <strong>noise was not something we could allow</strong>. Avishek and Nilanjan arrived at 10:00 PM, and the four of us had Chinese food for dinner 🙂</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>At 12:00 AM, work resumed</strong>. It was <em>amazing</em>! With each passing minute, we discovered newer and better ways to make and record foley sounds! I even tried to pan the microphone with Sreyan&#8217;s footsteps. Several effects were ready by 3:00 AM &#8211; <em>typing, blowing out a candle, walking, letter falling, sitting on an easy-chair, and several others</em>. But, by then, exhaustion was gradually creeping over the two of us. We decided to take a break, and talk for a while&#8230;</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify;\">The Date of Submission</h3>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The <strong>6:00 AM alarm</strong> on Sreyan&#8217;s cellphone woke the four of us. We had a few hours left before submission. <strong>Mayhem broke out inside our minds</strong>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Within half an hour, we recorded the remaining foley sounds &#8211; <em>knocking, writing, crumbling</em>, etc. Nilanjan utilized that time to download a track that contained firefly sounds.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">In the next half hour, I edited the foley tracks, and made them ready for use. Here are two foley sound-tracks:</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"166\" scrolling=\"no\" frameborder=\"no\" src=\"https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.soundcloud.com%2Ftracks%2F191147886%3Fsecret_token%3Ds-6r1KM\"></iframe> <span style=\"font-family:'Courier New';\">Blowing out a candle [Alternative <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/nabhoneel95/candle-flame-foley/s-6r1KM\">link on SoundCloud</a>]</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"166\" scrolling=\"no\" frameborder=\"no\" src=\"https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.soundcloud.com%2Ftracks%2F191148537%3Fsecret_token%3Ds-GSUQe\"></iframe> <span style=\"font-family:'Courier New';\">Typing [Alternative <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/nabhoneel95/final-typing/s-GSUQe\">link on SoundCloud</a>]</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">What followed that was two and a half hours of video editing by Avishek and Sreyan. Now that I&#8217;m recalling everything, I realize what level of expertise the two possess. Under the <strong>enormous </strong>pressure, they swiftly placed <strong>all </strong>the foley tracks, added a <strong>huge </strong>number of minor details, added credits, added the intro, and even corrected several portions!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">However, the music was not yet done. At 11:00 AM, Avishek asked me to connect my (musical) keyboard to my laptop, and stated</p>\n<blockquote><p>You have exactly five minutes. Watch the video and play, just play what you think is right, and play without any mistakes.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">I was not very satisfied with what I had done. The only thing that was good was the final music &#8211; <em>I Giorni</em><em> </em>by <em>Ludovico Einaudi. </em></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify;\">The Last Hour</h3>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>I pulled out the UPS</strong>, packed it in a bag (since the laptop battery wasn&#8217;t powerful enough to last for an hour).The four of us got ready. <strong>Nilanjan called a taxi</strong>. I packed in anything we would need. The <strong>video rendering process was initiated</strong>, and the three of us &#8211; Avishek, Nilanjan and myself &#8211; started off for St. Xavier&#8217;s College. We submitted the short film later that day.</p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"> We don&#8217;t know the results yet. The judges haven&#8217;t decided. 7 other colleges are competing against us. Our film wasn&#8217;t perfect. However, we all agreed something&#8230;</p>\n<blockquote><p>This was <strong>the craziest </strong>project we had all taken part in!</p></blockquote>\n<div id=\"movie\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">And, we had given in everything we had in the five days that were available to us. <span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe class='youtube-player' type='text/html' width='640' height='360' src='https://www.youtube.com/embed/uTHrVOFlng4?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;fs=1&#038;autohide=2&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;wmode=transparent' allowfullscreen='true' style='border:0;'></iframe></span></div>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Finally, before ending this post, here are some pictures:</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_854\" style=\"width: 710px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"854\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/02/09/the-experience-of-making-a-short-film/actor-and-director-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/actor-and-director1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"2048,1174\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Agnij Sur&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"actor and director\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/actor-and-director1.jpg?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/actor-and-director1.jpg?w=700\" class=\"size-large wp-image-854\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/actor-and-director1.jpg?w=700&#038;h=401\" alt=\"Sreyan and Sourya\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/actor-and-director1.jpg?w=700&amp;h=401 700w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/actor-and-director1.jpg?w=1400&amp;h=802 1400w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/actor-and-director1.jpg?w=150&amp;h=86 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/actor-and-director1.jpg?w=450&amp;h=258 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/actor-and-director1.jpg?w=768&amp;h=440 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"   /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sreyan and Sourya</figcaption></figure>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_852\" style=\"width: 710px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"852\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/02/09/the-experience-of-making-a-short-film/flame-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/flame1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"2048,1366\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Agnij Sur&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"flame\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/flame1.jpg?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/flame1.jpg?w=700\" class=\"size-large wp-image-852\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/flame1.jpg?w=700&#038;h=467\" alt=\"Sourya Sur Roy - the only face in the film\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/flame1.jpg?w=700&amp;h=467 700w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/flame1.jpg?w=1400&amp;h=934 1400w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/flame1.jpg?w=150&amp;h=100 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/flame1.jpg?w=450&amp;h=300 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/flame1.jpg?w=768&amp;h=512 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"   /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sourya Sur Roy &#8211; the only face in the film</figcaption></figure>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_818\" style=\"width: 710px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"818\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/02/09/the-experience-of-making-a-short-film/father/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/father.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"2048,1365\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Agnij Sur&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"father\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/father.jpg?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/father.jpg?w=700\" class=\"size-large wp-image-818\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/father.jpg?w=700&#038;h=467\" alt=\"Aritra Mitra\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/father.jpg?w=700&amp;h=467 700w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/father.jpg?w=1400&amp;h=934 1400w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/father.jpg?w=150&amp;h=100 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/father.jpg?w=450&amp;h=300 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/father.jpg?w=768&amp;h=512 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"   /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Aritra Mitra</figcaption></figure>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_851\" style=\"width: 710px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"851\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/02/09/the-experience-of-making-a-short-film/nilanjan-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/nilanjan1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"2048,1365\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Agnij Sur&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"nilanjan\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/nilanjan1.jpg?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/nilanjan1.jpg?w=700\" class=\"size-large wp-image-851\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/nilanjan1.jpg?w=700&#038;h=467\" alt=\"Nilanjan Banerjee\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/nilanjan1.jpg?w=700&amp;h=467 700w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/nilanjan1.jpg?w=1400&amp;h=934 1400w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/nilanjan1.jpg?w=150&amp;h=100 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/nilanjan1.jpg?w=450&amp;h=300 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/nilanjan1.jpg?w=768&amp;h=512 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"   /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Nilanjan Banerjee</figcaption></figure>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The joy in creating this short film transcended <strong>everything</strong>. And frankly, the decision of the judges won&#8217;t matter. We, <strong>The Anon. Productions, </strong>thoroughly enjoyed making our first short film. I&#8217;m happy. <strong>We&#8217;re </strong>happy.</p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Check out the Facebook page of <em><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/theanonproductions?fref=ts\">The Anon. Productions</a>, </em>and surely subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCtOWokDyMAxelvOTThTZ-UA\">YouTube channel</a>, for getting updates of our future projects.</p>\n<hr />\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify;\">Update:</h4>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">On the 19th of February, 2015, the judges did come to a decision. They decided to mark our work the best among the 7 short films that had been submitted. We won the competition. I&#8217;ll admit something. The victory didn&#8217;t matter much. However, this acknowledgement was a big form of<strong> </strong>encouragement for us. Thank you everyone &#8211; viewers and judges 🙂</p>\n","date":"2015-02-08T21:27:35.000Z","slug":"the-experience-of-making-a-short-film","excerpt":"<p>This was the craziest project we had all taken part in!<br />\nAnd, we had given in everything we had in the five days that were available to us</p>\n","jetpack_featured_media_url":""},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Nabhoneel's Parchments","subtitle":"All thing photographed and written down"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"6571a02c-6ea8-5f66-9e1a-aa11fa798d8f"}}